{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "05", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "05", "M": "53", "S": "31"}}, "news": [{"title": "Four illegal commercial buildings demolished in Ludhiana", "para": "Ludhiana's municipal corporation has intensified its drive against illegal constructions, demolishing four under-construction buildings across Zone D on Friday.  These structures were erected in clear defiance of building bylaws, even after official notices were issued.  Authorities are urging residents and developers to secure approved plans before commencing any construction to prevent similar enforcement actions.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/crackdown-on-illegal-buildings-in-ludhiana-four-structures-demolished/132191348?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-104456/132191348.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Arihant Foundations acquires land parcel in Chennai for \u20b9300 crore office project", "para": "Arihant Foundations & Housing has acquired over half an acre on Anna Salai, adjacent to Hyatt Regency Chennai. The company plans to develop a boutique Grade-A commercial office project with an estimated GDV of \u20b9300 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/arihant-foundations-launches-300-crore-office-project-in-chennai/132191342?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-927454/132191342.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Prime minister to lay foundation stone for Jaipur metro phase-II on July 4", "para": "Prime Minister Narendra Modi is inaugurating Phase II of the Jaipur Metro, a five-year project set to revolutionize connectivity along Tonk Road. This expansion includes a significant elevated stretch from Sitapura to Pinjrapole and an underground section near the airport.  Traffic management plans are in place to minimize disruption, with a focus on creating a 'Model Corridor' to ensure smooth commutes during construction.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/prime-minister-modi-to-launch-jaipur-metro-phase-ii-construction-on-july-4/132174484?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-185968/132174484.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}